import Home from './components/home/home'
import Login from './components/Login/login';

const routes =[
    {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Home",
        key: "home",
        route: "/home",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 0,
        sets: false,
        icon: "homeIcon.png"
    },
    {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Alphabet",
        key: "alphabet",
        route: "/alphabet",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 1,
        sets: true,
        icon: "alphIcon.PNG"
    },
    {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Vocabulary",
        key: "vocab",
        route: "/vocab",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 10,
        sets: true,
        icon: "wordIcon.png"
    },
    {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Sentences",
        key: "sent",
        route: "/sent",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 10,
        sets: true,
        icon: "sentenceIcon.png"
    },
    {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Tenses",
        key: "tense",
        route: "/tense",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 10,
        sets: true,
        icon: "tensesIcon.png"
    },
    {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Reading",
        key: "read",
        route: "/read",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 10,
        sets: true,
        icon: "readingIcon.png"
    },
    {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Writing",
        key: "write",
        route: "/write",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 0,
        sets: false,
        icon: "writingIcon.png"
    },
    {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Preferences",
        key: "preferences",
        route: "/preferences",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 0,
        bottom: true,
        sets: false,
        icon: "settingIcon.png"
    },
    {
        type: "collapse",
        name: "Preferences",
        key: "preferences",
        route: "/preferences",
        component: <Home />,
        noCollapse: true,
        completed_sets: 0,
        total_sets: 0,
        bottom: true,
        sets: false,
        icon: "settingIcon.png"
    }
];

export default routes;
